[[image:GiantHound.png||style="float: right;"]]Like their smaller cousins kept by humans these hounds serve as hunting animals for hill giants and sometimes other large humanoids.
== Tactics ==
Giant hounds attempt to attack targets in pairs so they can grip hold of the target and worry it to death.
